# Morph target — UNIFORM 1.5x scale of the compact octahedron in
# MorphCrystal.obj. Every half-extent grows by the same ratio:
#   apex (Y)     = 0.20  →  0.30   (Y range 0.20..0.80)
#   equator (XZ) = 0.15  →  0.225  (X/Z range 0.275..0.725)
#
# Aspect ratio preserved (still 1.33 tall-to-wide), so the morph blend
# looks like a uniform "breathing" rather than asymmetric distortion.

vt 0 0
vt 1 0
vt 0.5 1

# Same 6 vertices as base, all pushed outward by 1.5x.
v 0.500 0.800 0.500
v 0.725 0.500 0.500
v 0.500 0.500 0.725
v 0.275 0.500 0.500
v 0.500 0.500 0.275
v 0.500 0.200 0.500

# Identical face declarations to MorphCrystal.obj (same topology).
f 1/3 3/1 2/2
f 1/3 4/1 3/2
f 1/3 5/1 4/2
f 1/3 2/1 5/2
f 6/3 2/1 3/2
f 6/3 3/1 4/2
f 6/3 4/1 5/2
f 6/3 5/1 2/2
